  <brief_title>Study to Assess Platelet Dysfunction With Verify Now Assay</brief_title>
  <official_title>&quot;In-vitro Characterization of Platelet Dysfunction in Common Hematological Disorders Using the Verify Now Assay&quot;</official_title>
  <sponsors>
